00:09:44.230 --> 00:09:48.960
in what was then West
Berlin, at the state archives.

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:54.420 position:56%
Where can I see a copy of that book?

00:09:54.420 --> 00:09:56.550
And they said oh we have it.

00:09:56.550 --> 00:09:59.670
I said could you please
make me a copy?

00:09:59.670 --> 00:10:01.070
Yes, come back tomorrow.

00:10:01.070 --> 00:10:04.550
