there, they were making it

00:10:04.550 --> 00:10:08.810
and I quick rushed
directly to the airplane.

00:10:08.810 --> 00:10:16.640
When I got home, I decided I saw a
need for publication of that book

00:10:16.640 --> 00:10:18.770
