be adopted, etcetera.

00:26:45.720 --> 00:26:53.090
The big difference was unless
it was prohibited by the rules,

00:26:53.090 --> 00:26:56.500
Jews in Prussia could
adopt any name they wanted,

00:26:56.500 --> 00:27:01.080
that is not necessarily true in
some of the other German states.

00:27:01.080 --> 00:27:03.710
But it was in Prussia.

00:27:05.450 --> 00:27:15.400
