00:29:12.290 --> 00:29:19.310
in its second cellar has the
largest collection of yearbooks

00:29:19.310 --> 00:29:22.800
from high schools in the world.

00:29:22.800 --> 00:29:25.390
I know they have Scotland
for example

00:29:25.390 --> 00:29:29.870
and I don't know specifically but
I have every reason to believe

00:29:29.870 --> 00:29:33.060
