of the greatest collections

00:29:33.060 --> 00:29:37.440
of high school yearbooks
even from the United States.

00:29:37.440 --> 00:29:42.810
I spent many many days
in that second cellar

00:29:42.810 --> 00:29:47.580 position:56%
