00:30:02.580 --> 00:30:12.110
Their names, birth
dates, place of birth,

00:30:12.110 --> 00:30:16.590
fathers profession whether alive
or dead and fathers location,

00:30:16.590 --> 00:30:21.230
interestingly though not
the name of the father.

00:30:21.230 --> 00:30:28.260
And the last entry would be the
current situation of the boy

00:30:28.260 --> 00:30:35.950
when he had left the school
and if there's an asterisk next

00:30:35.950 --> 00:30:37.250
