they were consistent in,

00:30:39.660 --> 00:30:44.110
everybody in Prussia had to do
the same thing at the same time.

00:30:44.110 --> 00:30:51.040
And these yearbooks
were compiled until 1915

00:30:51.040 --> 00:30:54.900
