00:48:51.870 --> 00:49:00.110
Between German Jews and the
what I'll callmthe Russian Jews.

00:49:00.110 --> 00:49:07.430
And so they were not always
observant, not always knowledgeable

00:49:07.430 --> 00:49:11.190
but they didn't want to admit that.

00:49:11.190 --> 00:49:14.170
Most German Jews were
very proud of the fact

00:49:14.170 --> 00:49:17.160
that they did not speak Yiddish.

00:49:17.160 --> 00:49:22.610
Most Pol's and Jews did
speak Yiddish but especially

00:49:22.610 --> 00:49:27.180
