been reluctant to admit it.

00:49:27.180 --> 00:49:35.840
And there was always this tension
between reform and orthodox.

00:49:35.840 --> 00:49:43.010
They were both congregations
in the city of Posen,

00:49:43.010 --> 00:49:46.710
but the orthodox was larger.

00:49:48.270 --> 00:49:52.940
Nevertheless there were a
large number of professionals.

00:49:52.940 --> 00:49:58.680
Many of those professionals,
but not all, were reformed Jews.

00:49:58.680 --> 00:50:03.720
They were orthodox Jews who were
professionals even if we take

00:50:03.720 --> 00:50:09.480
out the rabbi's who of course
would be more heavily represented

00:50:09.480 --> 00:50:11.780
among orthodoxy.

00:50:14.560 --> 00:50:16.510
Any other, yes sir.

