00:51:10.800 --> 00:51:13.850
on German society, I
would recommend that book

00:51:13.850 --> 00:51:17.000
and by the way it's written
by a Christian, not by a Jew.

00:51:21.270 --> 00:51:30.640
Basically it's very difficult, if
