00:51:30.640 --> 00:51:36.210
from Germany obtained
Nobel Laureates,

00:51:36.210 --> 00:51:39.290
but also look at those
whose [foreign language],

00:51:39.290 --> 00:51:47.250
the faculty adviser of those who
won Nobel Prizes among Germans,

